        <detaileddescription>
<para>Scalar inner product for multi-bit RaBitQ. Extracts each code value in O(1) via 64-bit window read + shift + mask. Also serves as the tail handler for SIMD kernels via the <computeroutput>start</computeroutput> parameter. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
