        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Dispatch to the best available kernel for the given ex_bits.</para>
<para>Routing (compile-time): ex_bits == 1: specialized 1-bit kernel (AVX-512 &gt; AVX2 &gt; scalar) ex_bits &gt;= 2: bit-plane decomposition (AVX2+BMI2 &gt; scalar)</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>sign_bits</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>packed sign bits (1 bit/dim, standard byte packing) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ex_code</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>packed extra-bit codes (ex_bits bits/dim) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>rotated_q</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>rotated query vector (float[d]) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>d</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>dimensionality </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ex_bits</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>number of extra bits per dimension (nb_bits - 1) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cb</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>constant bias: -(2^ex_bits - 0.5) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>inner product value </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
